<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Time Manager</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --c1: #D2D2EB;
            --c2: #AA9D9F;
            --c3: #826D62;
            --c4: #585B4C;
            --c5: #2A2C24;
        }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #585B4C;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #D2D2EB;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(42, 44, 36, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #2A2C24;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .password-box {
            background-color: rgba(210, 210, 235, 0.3);
            border: 2px solid #826D62;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .password-box .label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #826D62;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .password-box .password {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #2A2C24;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            word-break: break-all;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .warning {
            background-color: rgba(170, 157, 159, 0.15);
            border-left: 4px solid #AA9D9F;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: #2A2C24;
        }
        .security-notice {
            background-color: rgba(130, 109, 98, 0.1);
            border-left: 4px solid #826D62;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: #2A2C24;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #D2D2EB;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #826D62;
        }
        .credentials-table {
            width: 100%;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
        .credentials-table td {
            padding: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(210, 210, 235, 0.5);
        }
        .credentials-table td:first-child {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #826D62;
            width: 30%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Welcome to Time Manager</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello {{ user.firstName }} {{ user.lastName }},</p>

            <p>An administrator has created an account for you on Time Manager. Below are your login credentials:</p>

            <table class="credentials-table">
                <tr>
                    <td>Username:</td>
                    <td><strong>{{ user.username }}</strong></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Email:</td>
                    <td><strong>{{ user.email }}</strong></td>
                </tr>
            </table>

            <div class="password-box">
                <div class="label">Your Temporary Password</div>
                <div class="password">{{ temporaryPassword }}</div>
            </div>

            <div class="warning">
                <strong>You must change this password at your first login</strong><br>
                For security reasons, you will be required to set a new password when you first log in to your account.
            </div>

            <div class="security-notice">
                <strong>Security recommendations:</strong>
                <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                    <li>Keep this password confidential</li>
                    <li>Do not share this email with anyone</li>
                    <li>Delete this email after changing your password</li>
                    <li>Choose a strong, unique password when changing it</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <p>If you have any questions or did not expect to receive this email, please contact your administrator immediately.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message from Time Manager.<br>
            Please do not reply to this email.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 10px;">
                <strong>Account created:</strong> {{ user.createdAt|date('Y-m-d H:i:s') }}
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
